  "texts": [
    "All studies were deemed minimal risk and exempt by the MIT Committee on the Use of Humans as Experimental Subjects (protocol E-5539).",
    "We excluded participants for inattentiveness (both before they entered the study, using an openended text response, and early on in the study before random assignment using an attention check item).",
    "All studies were preregistered (see aspredicted.org/RPG_RY9, aspredicted.org/HSD_41Q, aspredicted.org/KSN_PNL).",
    "Any non-pre-registered analyses are labeled \"post hoc\" and any deviations from the pre-registrations are reported.",
    "Conversational data from all participants, including those removed from our analyses, is available via web application."
  ],
